 Release Note ......::

 Touareg is the 4th album by Belgian producer Airwave. 17 tracks that are
 combining the early Aiwave sound integrated into his new current sound giving
 an excuisite blend of music including collaborations with artists from all
 kinds of ethnic origins. As a bonus  some of his classics have been re-recorded
 and reworked into a 2K8 outfit giving them a proper sound and mixing. From a
 chilling opening movie anthem to solid trance mixed with true anthemic melodies
 to even an experimental beats track.
